Tilson Says Buffett’s Berkshire Is ‘Cheapest We’ve Ever Seen It’

-- B y   N i k o l a j   G a m m e l t o f t
-- 
2011-10-18T18:10:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/tilson-says-buffett-s-berkshire-cheapest-we-ve-ever-seen-2-.html
Whitney Tilson , the co-founder of T2
Partners LLP, recommended investors buy  Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) ,
saying the shares are the “cheapest we’ve ever seen it.”  He spoke today in  New York  at the Value Investing Congress,
which he co-founded. Tilson said he’s owned shares of Warren Buffett’s Berkshire Hathaway for 13 years.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nikolaj Gammeltoft in New York at 
 ngammeltoft@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
